snippet.title: Death Elevator - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Death Elevator is a simple rouguelike fps where you go up an elevator killing waves of enemies while uncover what the f is happening

Make no mistakes because everything is fatal!

Follow me on twitter to know more about the project @FernandoTittz  
https://twitter.com/FernandoTittz

Join our discord to chat :D
https://discord.com/invite/peAk4fUr2c
